title: American Horror Stories Episode 2 The Rubber (Wo)Man Review Part 2
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Furthermore, by visiting on Halloween, Scarlett ensures that Ruby stays at the Murder House the one day she can leave. As for the rubber MAN, I think it was the same rubber man entity from outpost 3 in Apocalypse
Ruby knows she has time on her side. Scarlett will also want to see her Dads. She knows eventually she will probably want to stay.

“The ghosts all living like the Brady bunch in the murder house. Except for the ones from the original American horror story murder house…they I guess were not in the budget to be there so anyway” I died girl 😂😂😂
i loved the two first episodes can't wait for the rest of the season and season 10 of ahs

It was a little strange for me when I heard addys voice coming from the basement say ‘your gonna die in there’ when she died outside the house in season one allowing her to not be trapped there other than that no complaints 😁👍🏽
